profile:
The Home Improvement People have completed literally thousands of renovations since our inception. We are a unique award winning contracting company, consulted by various media as industry experts. 
Please view our website at homeimprovementpeople.com to view images of some of our projects. 
For our clients' convenience, we've implemented progress billing as well as financing.
Regardless of scope, we approach every single home renovation with a foundation of strong design aesthetics, comprehensive product options, sound project management, and a commitment to craftsmanship.
 
Our projects range from remodelled bathrooms and kitchens, to rear additions,  hardwood flooring, basements, second story additions and other extensive renovations. We undertake work in all budget ranges.
 
Choosing a reputable contractor is the most important decision you will make regarding your renovation. From plans and permits, to last little finishing details, The Home Improvement People is committed to completing your renovations and home improvements in a professional manner and to your complete satisfaction.
We take pride in our personalized service and our high quality workmanship. 
Call us for quality, insured work - completed on time, and on budget.
416-782-7605.

profile:
"Why replace when we can paint"

A Woman's Touch Cabinet Painting is a professional painting company that is owned and operated by women. We take pride in the quality of our work and we pay the utmost attention to detail. 
We service Toronto, Richmond Hill, Newmarket, Aurora, Markham, Stouffville, Vaughan, Mississauga, Etobicoke, Barrie, Pickering, Oshawa, York Region, GTA and surrounding areas.

No matter the wood; pine, maple, oak or even melamine, we can paint most cabinet surfaces to give you the new look you desire.

STEPS:

-FIRST STEP
We will come and remove all facings from your cabinets, doors and drawers.
They will get loaded up to go back to our state of the art facility to sprayed in a spray booth.

-SECOND STEP
While we are there, we will then spend the day proceeding to tape off your entire kitchen, ceilings, walls, floors, countertops, back splash and every place we have removed a facing.

-THIRD STEP
We will then spray all the sides, gables, kick plates, crown molding and any other fixed area that requires painting.

-FOURTH STEP
We then take everything down and we are gone for approximately 2 weeks spraying your doors.

-FIFTH STEP
Then we return and reinstall your doors.

We use a water based, Low VOC lacquer. We do not use high odor, and flammable paints.

The entire process takes approximately 2 weeks, but you will have full use of your kitchen the day after we spray on site.

The Smart Alternative to Cabinet Painters
Many professional cabinet painters apply a layer or two of paint to change the color and call it a day. N-Hance’s cabinet refinishing process, on the other hand, does more than just cover up an old look with a new one. N-Hance cabinet refinishers thoroughly cleans and primes the cabinets, ensuring the best adhesive surface.

Unlike traditional cabinet painters who often leave the grain of the wood exposed, N-Hance Wood Refinishing Aurora Newmarket cabinet refinishers offer a solution that will minimize the grain and give your cabinets a cleaner, on-trend appearance. And while it can take over a week for cabinet painters to complete their work and let it dry, our Lightspeed® process cures the finish immediately!
Custom Color Finishes
N-Hance Wood Refinishing Aurora Newmarket's line of Opaque Cabinet Finishes saturate the wood with rich, beautiful color while allowing the natural beauty of the grain to remain visible. Opaque Fin.
Cabinet Door Replacement
Sometimes, you’re ready for a completely new look in your kitchen or bathroom, but the existing cabinets are in perfectly good condition. Rather than waste time and money on a complete kitchen remodel, you can give your cabinets a fresh, new look with N-Hance Wood Refinishing Aurora Newmarket’s Cabinet Door Replacement service!
Cabinet Refacing Service
Often, when people want to update their homes, the first thought is to rip out and replace the cabinets. This can lead to an unnecessarily messy and expensive project. Cabinet refacing is one alternative to consider, but when you decide that you want to update the cabinets in your kitchen, N-Hance’s® cabinet refinishing brings the best value and results. Rather than replacing the entire cabinet unit or refacing with new cabinet doors, you can simply update the outside to make it look fresh and brand new.
